WEBVTT

00:00:07.100 --> 00:00:11.850
=Recruit A General to Lead the Troops=

00:00:12.037 --> 00:00:14.887
=Episode 6=

00:00:18.150 --> 00:00:19.340
Hey.

00:00:20.790 --> 00:00:21.669
What are you doing?

00:00:21.670 --> 00:00:23.540
Why is it always fighting and killing?

00:00:27.710 --> 00:00:30.860
Do all Death Servants have unique marks?

00:00:31.350 --> 00:00:32.620
Courting death.

00:00:34.690 --> 00:00:35.589
Why did you not dodge?

00:00:35.590 --> 00:00:36.549
How could I dodge?

00:00:36.550 --> 00:00:38.660
You are a martial master. I am not.

00:00:39.510 --> 00:00:40.660
Hey.

00:00:40.790 --> 00:00:42.540
It is this mark.

00:00:49.990 --> 00:00:51.740
I am really curious.

00:00:51.950 --> 00:00:53.600
You are a Death Servant,

00:00:53.600 --> 00:00:55.889
so how did you become
the Fourth Boss of Qingfeng Stronghold?

00:00:55.889 --> 00:00:56.940
None of your concern.

00:00:58.150 --> 00:00:58.949
You will not say?

00:00:58.950 --> 00:01:00.749
If you will not,
I will go find Chen Xinrou.

00:01:00.750 --> 00:01:01.949
I will tell her

00:01:01.950 --> 00:01:04.629
that her Fourth Boss
only pretends to be loyal,

00:01:04.630 --> 00:01:06.989
when in truth she is a Death Servant
of unknown origin.

00:01:06.990 --> 00:01:08.620
I will have her drive you out.

00:01:09.790 --> 00:01:11.780
She will never believe such nonsense.

00:01:12.790 --> 00:01:14.620
She may not have before,

00:01:14.630 --> 00:01:17.780
but just now Shihou Stronghold sent
Death Servants into Qingfeng Stronghold.

00:01:17.790 --> 00:01:19.429
And you just happen to be one yourself.

00:01:19.430 --> 00:01:21.140
Do you not think she will suspect you?

00:01:21.190 --> 00:01:23.549
And once suspicion arises,

00:01:23.550 --> 00:01:25.140
the charge will stand.

00:01:25.150 --> 00:01:27.149
At that point, whether you are or not,

00:01:27.150 --> 00:01:28.700
she will cast you out.

00:01:30.790 --> 00:01:32.340
I cannot leave.

00:01:32.910 --> 00:01:33.989
Cannot leave?

00:01:33.990 --> 00:01:34.789
Why not?

00:01:34.790 --> 00:01:36.980
I am her Shadow.

00:01:37.550 --> 00:01:40.700
My purpose in life is to protect her.

00:01:41.070 --> 00:01:42.780
A Shadow must not be seen.

00:01:43.350 --> 00:01:44.540
That is the rule.

00:01:45.990 --> 00:01:48.220
Then how did you become her Shadow?

00:01:48.790 --> 00:01:50.149
You ask too many questions.

00:01:50.150 --> 00:01:50.989
Still not speaking?

00:01:50.990 --> 00:01:52.549
Then I will tell her.

00:01:52.550 --> 00:01:53.700
Stop.

00:01:55.550 --> 00:01:58.549
Wealthy nobles
choose children without parents

00:01:58.550 --> 00:01:59.789
and train them as Death Servants,

00:01:59.790 --> 00:02:00.869
to serve them.

00:02:00.870 --> 00:02:02.540
I was one of those.

00:02:04.350 --> 00:02:05.500
Then,

00:02:06.690 --> 00:02:07.949
what did they have you do?

00:02:07.950 --> 00:02:09.300
Kill.

00:02:11.270 --> 00:02:12.949
The Leader's father chose me

00:02:12.950 --> 00:02:14.589
to be her only Death Servant.

00:02:14.590 --> 00:02:17.500
Then how did you become the Fourth Boss?

00:02:22.870 --> 00:02:24.020
That year,

00:02:25.530 --> 00:02:27.709
the Leader fled
from her marriage into the outskirts.

00:02:27.710 --> 00:02:29.100
She accidentally fell into the water.

00:02:29.710 --> 00:02:31.220
Later, as you know,

00:02:31.590 --> 00:02:33.900
she was captured by Shihou Stronghold.

00:02:34.030 --> 00:02:35.620
Bullied day after day.

00:02:39.030 --> 00:02:40.780
And I could not reveal myself
to save her.

00:02:40.990 --> 00:02:42.589
I am a Death Servant.

00:02:42.590 --> 00:02:44.340
My heart should feel no pain.

00:02:45.270 --> 00:02:47.220
But when I saw her being bullied,

00:02:47.270 --> 00:02:49.100
my heart twisted like a knife.

00:02:49.390 --> 00:02:50.549
I revealed myself

00:02:50.550 --> 00:02:51.900
and protected her.

00:02:52.030 --> 00:02:55.060
That day, I was ready to leave.

00:02:56.990 --> 00:02:58.340
Heroine.

00:02:59.550 --> 00:03:00.900
Stay with us.

00:03:01.310 --> 00:03:03.180
Let us be good friends from now on.

00:03:09.310 --> 00:03:11.660
She is the only one
who treats me like family.

00:03:11.950 --> 00:03:13.749
So I must protect her,

00:03:13.750 --> 00:03:15.780
and never let anyone hurt her.

00:03:16.270 --> 00:03:18.740
It is best she never learns of this.

00:03:18.750 --> 00:03:20.900
So you must not reveal a single word.

00:03:21.750 --> 00:03:24.060
Do not worry, I will not tell.

00:03:24.430 --> 00:03:25.709
She sees you as a sister,

00:03:25.710 --> 00:03:27.340
I see you as a brother.

00:03:27.430 --> 00:03:30.220
And between brothers,
there must be trust.

00:03:38.550 --> 00:03:39.989
My dear Leader,

00:03:39.990 --> 00:03:42.300
how could you let them stay?

00:03:42.550 --> 00:03:44.549
Having one man in the stronghold

00:03:44.550 --> 00:03:46.149
was already annoying enough.

00:03:46.150 --> 00:03:47.029
Now look at this,

00:03:47.030 --> 00:03:48.549
there are four more.

00:03:48.550 --> 00:03:49.940
If this continues,

00:03:49.990 --> 00:03:51.940
our stronghold will turn
into a den of men.

00:03:52.150 --> 00:03:54.740
If Li Chengyu wants them here,
then let them stay.

00:03:57.390 --> 00:03:58.500
Leader.

00:03:59.030 --> 00:04:01.900
Do you truly
have feelings for Li Chengyu?

00:04:03.310 --> 00:04:04.620
How could that be?

00:04:06.150 --> 00:04:10.580
Was it not you who said marrying a husband
would be good for the stronghold?

00:04:15.170 --> 00:04:16.507
(Qingfeng Stronghold.
Yuchang Hot Springs)

00:04:17.350 --> 00:04:20.260
Beautiful sisters, come take a look.

00:04:21.230 --> 00:04:23.429
Step right up and see for yourselves.

00:04:23.430 --> 00:04:25.669
Do you all feel itchy?

00:04:25.670 --> 00:04:27.183
By chance, my brother

00:04:27.184 --> 00:04:29.440
(Yuchang Hot Springs)
has just built the Yuchang Hot Springs.

00:04:29.440 --> 00:04:30.780
Yeah. Yuchang Hot Springs.

00:04:31.030 --> 00:04:32.620
As the name suggests,

00:04:32.670 --> 00:04:36.060
it is a place for bathing and changing.

00:04:37.230 --> 00:04:38.469
Hot water in abundance.

00:04:38.470 --> 00:04:40.029
You may bathe and soak.

00:04:40.030 --> 00:04:41.469
Snacks are plentiful.

00:04:41.470 --> 00:04:42.669
So what are you waiting for?

00:04:42.670 --> 00:04:44.229
Come inside and enjoy a bath.

00:04:44.230 --> 00:04:46.580
Blow bubbles, splash water.

00:04:49.150 --> 00:04:51.060
Hey, all of you, come here.

00:04:52.550 --> 00:04:55.340
Hey, hey, do not leave.

00:04:57.150 --> 00:04:59.229
You would dare
enter a place built by men?

00:04:59.230 --> 00:05:01.909
Is it not filthy?
Are you not afraid of the stench?

00:05:01.910 --> 00:05:03.349
Disperse, all of you.

00:05:03.350 --> 00:05:05.500
Go about your business, quickly.

00:05:09.910 --> 00:05:11.029
Qiu Erniang.

00:05:11.030 --> 00:05:13.989
Even Chen Xinrou did not interfere,
so why are you making trouble here?

00:05:13.990 --> 00:05:15.109
And you dare call me filthy?

00:05:15.110 --> 00:05:17.700
I say you are the one
who is filthy for not bathing.

00:05:18.110 --> 00:05:20.060
You must not offend Erniang.

00:05:20.230 --> 00:05:21.709
Back in the day, her man

00:05:21.710 --> 00:05:23.989
was a minor leader
of Qingfeng Stronghold.

00:05:23.990 --> 00:05:25.669
At that time, Liu Pitang was the Leader.

00:05:25.670 --> 00:05:28.349
In order to please Liu Pitang,

00:05:28.350 --> 00:05:30.940
that minor leader
offered Erniang to him.

00:05:31.350 --> 00:05:32.429
That very night,

00:05:32.430 --> 00:05:33.469
a bolt of lightning

00:05:33.470 --> 00:05:37.020
struck down
and killed her man on the spot.

00:05:37.230 --> 00:05:38.549
When Liu Pitang saw it,

00:05:38.550 --> 00:05:41.580
he thought, this woman is ominous.

00:05:41.590 --> 00:05:42.940
So he dared not touch her.

00:05:43.350 --> 00:05:45.229
From then on,

00:05:45.230 --> 00:05:47.549
Erniang came to despise men.

00:05:47.550 --> 00:05:48.589
And men in turn

00:05:48.590 --> 00:05:50.349
did not dare to go near her,

00:05:50.350 --> 00:05:52.140
fearing a terrible death.

00:05:52.350 --> 00:05:54.349
No wonder she is so wild,

00:05:54.350 --> 00:05:55.940
and hates men so deeply.

00:05:57.790 --> 00:05:59.500
How do you know this so clearly?

00:05:59.590 --> 00:06:00.349
Do you like her?

00:06:00.350 --> 00:06:01.900
Hahaha, brother,

00:06:01.990 --> 00:06:03.229
what are you saying?

00:06:03.230 --> 00:06:04.589
Even if I did like her,

00:06:04.590 --> 00:06:05.989
I am timid.

00:06:05.990 --> 00:06:07.340
I fear death.

00:06:07.590 --> 00:06:08.589
In those years,

00:06:08.590 --> 00:06:11.349
I was just a water-carrying bandit
in Qingfeng Stronghold.

00:06:11.350 --> 00:06:13.709
Relying on my cleverness,

00:06:13.710 --> 00:06:17.349
I rose step by step
to become the Second Boss.

00:06:17.350 --> 00:06:18.109
Come, applaud.

00:06:18.110 --> 00:06:20.669
Applaud, hahaha.

00:06:20.670 --> 00:06:22.429
So if you want to open this hot spring,

00:06:22.430 --> 00:06:24.340
you must first deal with Qiu Erniang.

00:06:24.590 --> 00:06:27.460
But handling Erniang is no easy task.

00:06:30.790 --> 00:06:33.469
She trusts no one.
She believes only in fate.

00:06:33.470 --> 00:06:35.700
Every time she delivers goods
down the mountain,

00:06:35.990 --> 00:06:37.909
she goes to
the Matchmaker Temple to pray.

00:06:37.910 --> 00:06:39.700
Matchmaker Temple?

00:06:40.670 --> 00:06:43.820
Tomorrow, she will deliver
another batch of goods.

00:06:45.230 --> 00:06:46.589
Why are you helping me?

00:06:46.590 --> 00:06:48.460
Do you like me?

00:06:51.670 --> 00:06:52.669
Brother.

00:06:52.670 --> 00:06:53.789
This Erniang,

00:06:53.790 --> 00:06:55.109
she hates men so much.

00:06:55.110 --> 00:06:56.709
Why does she go
to the Matchmaker Temple?

00:06:56.710 --> 00:06:58.407
(Matchmaker Temple.)

00:06:58.590 --> 00:06:59.789
(The more she despises men,)

00:06:59.790 --> 00:07:01.580
(the more she longs for one.)

00:07:09.350 --> 00:07:10.500
This fortune slip.

00:07:12.030 --> 00:07:13.380
Congratulations, young lady.

00:07:14.470 --> 00:07:15.909
This is the best of fortunes.

00:07:15.910 --> 00:07:18.029
Your destined one will soon arrive.

00:07:18.030 --> 00:07:19.700
When you return home,

00:07:20.710 --> 00:07:22.780
at the moment you step inside the gate,

00:07:22.790 --> 00:07:25.220
walk straight for fifty steps,

00:07:25.350 --> 00:07:28.229
then turn east for thirty more,

00:07:28.230 --> 00:07:29.549
and enter the house.

00:07:29.550 --> 00:07:31.700
There you will meet your destined one.

00:07:33.670 --> 00:07:35.820
Thank you, Master.

00:07:45.110 --> 00:07:47.020
Old man, much obliged.

00:07:48.030 --> 00:07:50.380
General Li, you are too polite.

00:08:06.150 --> 00:08:08.140
(What is that smell on these clothes?)

00:08:39.870 --> 00:08:42.420
Welcome, Second Boss,
to give your guidance.

00:08:43.190 --> 00:08:44.229
I never expected

00:08:44.230 --> 00:08:47.189
the first guest of the hot spring
would be you, Second Boss.

00:08:47.190 --> 00:08:49.220
Let me show you around.

00:08:49.470 --> 00:08:50.869
This large pool behind me,

00:08:50.870 --> 00:08:52.469
that is the hot spring area.

00:08:52.470 --> 00:08:54.709
It is where the ladies may bathe.

00:08:54.710 --> 00:08:56.060
Now, look this way.

00:08:58.070 --> 00:08:59.349
Behind this curtain

00:08:59.350 --> 00:09:01.820
is where the ladies change clothes.

00:09:02.110 --> 00:09:03.300
Follow me.

00:09:04.470 --> 00:09:05.469
Here is a mirror.

00:09:05.470 --> 00:09:06.709
Cosmetics are over here.

00:09:06.710 --> 00:09:07.629
This side

00:09:07.630 --> 00:09:09.869
is for the ladies to freshen up

00:09:09.870 --> 00:09:11.660
and put on their make-up again.

00:09:12.710 --> 00:09:14.460
And here is even better.

00:09:16.230 --> 00:09:17.469
There is a shower area,

00:09:17.470 --> 00:09:19.100
and a place for scrubbing.

00:09:26.710 --> 00:09:29.340
Second Boss.

00:09:29.870 --> 00:09:31.740
Let me ask you something.

00:09:32.110 --> 00:09:34.420
If you do not like someone,

00:09:34.470 --> 00:09:35.820
and even dislike him greatly,

00:09:36.710 --> 00:09:41.749
but fate has arranged
that he is your destined one,

00:09:41.750 --> 00:09:43.540
what would you choose?

00:09:45.630 --> 00:09:47.060
I would choose to accept fate.

00:09:47.190 --> 00:09:49.820
But I truly detest that person.

00:09:49.870 --> 00:09:52.580
Fate is the greatest
of all arrangements.

00:10:01.230 --> 00:10:02.749
Forgive me, Leader.

00:10:02.750 --> 00:10:06.540
Let us bathe together.

00:10:07.870 --> 00:10:08.869
Second Boss.

00:10:08.870 --> 00:10:10.589
That is not what I meant.

00:10:10.590 --> 00:10:13.460
Sometimes fate depends on the person.

00:10:14.870 --> 00:10:16.340
Yulang.

00:10:18.110 --> 00:10:21.869
(Qingfeng Stronghold, Yuchang Hot Springs)
Beautiful ladies, come and see.

00:10:21.870 --> 00:10:23.300
Take a look.

00:10:23.470 --> 00:10:27.509
Your Second Boss
is already inside, bathing.

00:10:27.510 --> 00:10:29.509
Blowing bubbles and splashing about.

00:10:29.510 --> 00:10:31.229
What are you still waiting for?

00:10:31.230 --> 00:10:32.109
Say it.

00:10:32.110 --> 00:10:33.940
Welcome.

00:10:34.350 --> 00:10:36.740
Welcome.

00:10:37.310 --> 00:10:38.660
Make some bubbles.

00:10:39.230 --> 00:10:40.540
Blow some bubbles.

00:10:59.630 --> 00:11:02.300
Between these two mountains
there is only one river.

00:11:02.470 --> 00:11:04.229
And that Qingfeng Stronghold

00:11:04.230 --> 00:11:05.700
has been taken by them.

00:11:05.710 --> 00:11:07.229
I have not bathed for half a year.

00:11:07.230 --> 00:11:08.420
It itches terribly.

00:11:08.830 --> 00:11:11.469
Tell me, those women in that stronghold,

00:11:11.470 --> 00:11:12.740
what did they build?

00:11:13.350 --> 00:11:15.460
Yuchang Hot Springs.

00:11:15.950 --> 00:11:17.829
It was Cold Tiger and Li Chengyu.

00:11:17.830 --> 00:11:19.629
They dug through
the well at Qingfeng's gate.

00:11:19.630 --> 00:11:21.469
What?

00:11:21.470 --> 00:11:22.709
Huzi did not die?

00:11:22.710 --> 00:11:23.629
No.

00:11:23.630 --> 00:11:24.629
Go.

00:11:24.630 --> 00:11:27.469
Find someone to finish him off for me.

00:11:27.470 --> 00:11:29.109
Half a month's work,

00:11:29.110 --> 00:11:32.069
and today is
the Best Stronghold Member Ceremony.

00:11:32.070 --> 00:11:34.940
The award can belong to no one but me.

00:11:38.070 --> 00:11:40.740
Is that not Shihou Stronghold?

00:11:41.390 --> 00:11:44.420
Damn, that is
the well linked to my hot spring.

00:11:44.630 --> 00:11:46.180
They have ruined my plan.

00:11:54.310 --> 00:11:55.460
Do not run.

00:11:59.750 --> 00:12:00.940
Mischievous.

00:12:01.830 --> 00:12:03.060
So mischievous.

00:12:09.870 --> 00:12:12.989
Chengyu, this Yuchang Hot Springs
is truly delightful.

00:12:12.990 --> 00:12:15.940
It seems men are not entirely useless.

00:12:16.470 --> 00:12:18.469
No wonder the Leader kept them here.

00:12:18.470 --> 00:12:21.180
Yes, though our monthly
expenses have risen.

00:12:22.830 --> 00:12:25.709
But I think Chengyu
is really a good man.

00:12:25.710 --> 00:12:29.109
Not only did he build this hot spring
for everyone's benefit,

00:12:29.110 --> 00:12:31.420
he also asks for no silver in return.

00:12:32.310 --> 00:12:35.589
A few days ago he asked me
about the Best Stronghold Member.

00:12:35.590 --> 00:12:38.540
Why is he doing all this?

00:12:39.470 --> 00:12:43.340
He went to such lengths
to build Yuchang Hot Springs.

00:12:43.350 --> 00:12:44.589
There must be a reason.

00:12:44.590 --> 00:12:45.980
Sisters,

00:12:46.190 --> 00:12:49.340
perhaps you could find
a chance to test him for me.

00:12:49.390 --> 00:12:51.420
How should we test him?

00:12:53.590 --> 00:12:54.940
I do not know either.

00:12:56.350 --> 00:12:57.820
Oh, stop fooling around.

00:13:04.390 --> 00:13:05.660
Sorry, sorry.

00:13:07.190 --> 00:13:09.620
(Wait, did I just see...)

00:13:33.710 --> 00:13:37.309
♪If you've never seen a bloom,
you can't know hope♪

00:13:37.310 --> 00:13:41.109
♪If you weren't here,
I wouldn't have come♪

00:13:41.110 --> 00:13:44.709
♪On a soda-lit night,
only the wind knows my love♪

00:13:44.710 --> 00:13:48.309
♪It's a helpless kind of feeling♪

00:13:48.310 --> 00:13:52.109
♪Like a feather of morning love
falling into the deep sea♪

00:13:52.110 --> 00:13:55.709
♪Being unnoticed,
yet I still tell you I love you♪

00:13:55.710 --> 00:13:59.509
♪But my confession
is drowned out by the wind♪

00:13:59.510 --> 00:14:02.309
♪You can't hear it♪

00:14:02.310 --> 00:14:04.709
♪I also want to rush forward♪

00:14:04.710 --> 00:14:06.709
♪To give you all my heart♪

00:14:06.710 --> 00:14:09.709
♪Yet it's pushed away by you♪

00:14:09.710 --> 00:14:12.309
♪Whether love is spoken
or left unspoken♪

00:14:12.310 --> 00:14:14.109
♪I know you understand♪

00:14:14.110 --> 00:14:16.909
♪It's just an accident♪

00:14:16.910 --> 00:14:20.909
♪You longed to wander once more,
by my side through the throng♪

00:14:20.910 --> 00:14:24.509
♪I know you weren't really here for me♪

00:14:24.510 --> 00:14:28.309
♪Yet still, who else could bring
a surprise quite like you♪

00:14:28.310 --> 00:14:31.509
♪After you left,
I didn't want to let go♪

00:14:31.510 --> 00:14:35.709
♪You brushed past me,
leaving your trace in the crowd♪

00:14:35.710 --> 00:14:38.909
♪I didn't shut you out♪

00:14:38.910 --> 00:14:41.109
♪But I couldn't wait for you to stop♪

00:14:41.110 --> 00:14:47.460
♪Yet I seem to clutch you,
unable to let you fade into the crowd♪